WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.517 --> 00:00:03.318
The one who will survive is the 
 one who has clear vision

00:00:03.788 --> 00:00:05.352
for what he wants and how he wants it.

00:00:05.352 --> 00:00:10.000
At the beginning, I gave an example of saint 
 who had that. That saint is Josemaría Escrivá.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.172
We have to be familiar

00:00:12.172 --> 00:00:13.423
with our vocation

00:00:13.799 --> 00:00:18.558
and we have to experience that God called 
 us to it in our hearts. Then, we will not give up.

00:00:18.558 --> 00:00:22.565
When he was very young priest, during 
 an apparition, God told him that he wants

00:00:22.565 --> 00:00:23.993
him to establish

00:00:23.993 --> 00:00:28.435
a congregation of lay people, who 
 will live holy through daily duties.

00:00:28.921 --> 00:00:35.741
Fathers, mothers, craftsmen, merchants, 
 doctors, politicians who live holy in daily life.

00:00:36.615 --> 00:00:38.982
Ten years from establishment, 
 there was no success.

00:00:39.827 --> 00:00:43.989
He even had to pretend to be 
 insane to save his life.

00:00:43.989 --> 00:00:48.168
He pretended to be insane like David. 
 It is described in The Books of Samuel.

00:00:48.168 --> 00:00:52.559
Just to save his life, he was hearing confessions 
 in parks, without wearing a collar or a stole.

00:00:52.559 --> 00:00:54.056
He was running away from the police

00:00:54.995 --> 00:01:00.190
because, during the Spanish Civil War 
 in Madrid, a Marxist leftist group

00:01:00.190 --> 00:01:03.182
was operating to persecute priests.

00:01:03.182 --> 00:01:05.857
He fled across the Pyrenees

00:01:06.608 --> 00:01:09.542
with the group of ten people 
 and they came to Rome.

00:01:09.542 --> 00:01:11.320
He was trying to establish a congregation there.

00:01:11.320 --> 00:01:14.877
All this time he was pushed forward 
 by that vision that God gave him.

00:01:14.877 --> 00:01:18.074
The problem of fathers and families of 
 today is that they don’t have the clear

00:01:18.074 --> 00:01:20.000
vision of where they are heading to.

00:01:22.317 --> 00:01:27.711
They don’t know where do they have 
 to go, they don’t have a clear, specific goal.

00:01:32.863 --> 00:01:35.415
And they can’t have it 
 until they discover the One

00:01:35.415 --> 00:01:37.825
who put them in a specific 
 situation or a place for a reason.

00:01:37.825 --> 00:01:40.125
Escrivá discovered that

00:01:40.125 --> 00:01:41.714
vision has to be very specific.

00:01:41.714 --> 00:01:43.714
It can’t be dispersed.

00:01:43.714 --> 00:01:46.688
I watched a movie that was made

00:01:47.752 --> 00:01:52.659
after an event when ten nuclear warheads 
 from the former Soviet Union disappeared.

00:01:53.787 --> 00:01:57.299
And a CIA agent said one sentence 
 that I remembered very well:

00:01:57.299 --> 00:02:00.710
„I'm not afraid of this man“ 
 (because they traced the money)

00:02:00.710 --> 00:02:06.367
„who bought ten nuclear warheads. I am 
 terribly scared of the one who bought only one

00:02:07.761 --> 00:02:10.559
because that man knows where to use it.”

00:02:12.332 --> 00:02:16.073
The people who know where they are going and 
 what they are doing are dangerous to the devil.

00:02:16.073 --> 00:02:16.780
Such was Escrivá.

00:02:16.780 --> 00:02:20.208
We have to have clear vision even when 
 external circumstances indicate that it

00:02:20.208 --> 00:02:21.406
is not possible.

00:02:23.065 --> 00:02:24.706
To have a clear vision.

00:02:24.706 --> 00:02:30.000
Solomon says in Proverbs 29:18: 
 „Where there is no vision, the people perish.”

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:32.000
When there is no vision, the family parish.

00:02:33.219 --> 00:02:35.435
Where are we taking them, specifically?

00:02:36.245 --> 00:02:40.675
We must learn to distinguish between 
 good deeds and God's works.

00:02:40.675 --> 00:02:44.436
There is a lot of good that we do, 
 but we don't have to do everything.

00:02:45.495 --> 00:02:47.810
What does God inspire us to do?

00:02:47.810 --> 00:02:52.100
How can a man be the leader of his 
 family if he is not first led by Christ?

00:02:52.913 --> 00:02:55.398
He can’t! These are his futile attempts

00:02:55.398 --> 00:02:58.965
that children will recognize as 
 such and go into disobedience.

00:03:00.255 --> 00:03:04.537
But if it is inspired by God, God 
 gives that authority to be obeyed.

00:03:08.693 --> 00:03:15.841
The prophet Isaiah wrote in one text that all 
 our good works are before God as dirty rags.

00:03:15.841 --> 00:03:17.514
And the Greek translation

00:03:17.514 --> 00:03:20.770
for dirty cloths says veste 
 menstrualis – used pads.

00:03:20.770 --> 00:03:22.797
Such are our good deeds.

00:03:22.797 --> 00:03:26.048
And we  must make a good distinction 
 about what God is calling us to do.

00:03:26.048 --> 00:03:29.470
I, as a community leader, also 
 have to keep an eye on this

00:03:29.470 --> 00:03:31.438
because there are thousands of offers coming.

00:03:31.438 --> 00:03:36.926
Get involved in this initiative, that 
 initiative, the caritas, the unborn,

00:03:36.926 --> 00:03:38.487
the worship groups...

00:03:38.487 --> 00:03:40.864
These are all good things and holy things,

00:03:40.864 --> 00:03:45.693
but if they don’t fit into our vision we received 
 from the Lord at the beginning of the year,

00:03:46.476 --> 00:03:47.726
then we reject those offers.

00:03:48.101 --> 00:03:50.617
And so we need to know how to prioritize.

00:03:51.180 --> 00:03:55.070
An emotionally healthy person will keep in balance

00:03:56.843 --> 00:04:00.401
his personal relationships, which he 
 should have with his loved ones,

00:04:00.401 --> 00:04:04.532
a relationship with God, work and 
 ministry, and time for rest,

00:04:04.532 --> 00:04:08.276
as much as possible. It's not even 
 possible to keep it in perfect balance,

00:04:08.276 --> 00:04:10.144
but he will keep an eye on it.

00:04:11.459 --> 00:04:14.450
And whoever believes this, God will 
 put him in charge of many more things.

00:04:14.450 --> 00:04:16.079
Jesus says: „Whoever is faithful with very little

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:18.355
will also be faithful with much.”

00:04:18.355 --> 00:04:21.557
And for those who work for employers,

00:04:21.557 --> 00:04:23.435
Jesus says: „Whoever is 
 faithful to someone else’s,

00:04:23.435 --> 00:04:24.992
he well be given his own.“

00:04:26.100 --> 00:04:31.398
And really, so many experiences from the people 
 who were in awe of the work they have,

00:04:31.398 --> 00:04:33.022
even though it was owned by someone else.

00:04:34.318 --> 00:04:37.685
And God really trusted them to get into 
 blessing. These are the spiritual laws

00:04:37.685 --> 00:04:40.311
Jesus places on all of us.

00:04:43.744 --> 00:04:46.261
Good deeds - works of God.

00:04:47.828 --> 00:04:49.472
A clear vision.

00:04:49.472 --> 00:04:51.464
A clear vision is the key to success.

00:04:52.408 --> 00:04:57.444
A man who knows where he is going 
 will instill confidence in those he leads.

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:01.779
A good friend of mine was

00:05:04.099 --> 00:05:08.008
one of the officers in the Operation Storm,

00:05:08.008 --> 00:05:11.495
and he told me about the experience 
 when Operation Storm was being prepared.

00:05:11.495 --> 00:05:15.163
Nobody knew exactly when it would 
 happen to keep the information secret.

00:05:15.783 --> 00:05:19.049
And he said that there was one place 
 near Udbina, which still exists today,

00:05:19.049 --> 00:05:20.395
but it was unfortunately abandoned.

00:05:20.395 --> 00:05:21.519
Široka kula,

00:05:21.519 --> 00:05:26.887
where Chetniks entered and killed the 
 whole place - 44 people. And the place

00:05:26.887 --> 00:05:28.859
ceased to exist, it was just their

00:05:28.859 --> 00:05:31.561
strategic point for military action.

00:05:32.613 --> 00:05:35.002
He had a hundred men under him

00:05:35.002 --> 00:05:40.240
and sent three of them into 
 the reconnaissance patrol.

00:05:42.507 --> 00:05:45.935
They inspected the terrain and there 
 was nothing there, but on the way back,

00:05:45.935 --> 00:05:47.656
one of them stepped on a landmine.

00:05:47.656 --> 00:05:53.438
Two of them came back in panic and said: 
 “There he is, alive, lying, bleeding, what should we do?”

00:05:53.438 --> 00:05:56.694
And the officer was thinking about what 
 he should do, he entered into this agony.

00:05:56.694 --> 00:06:00.182
The man was still alive, he knew he was still alive, 
 and again he would have risked if they went there.

00:06:00.182 --> 00:06:05.728
And he said: “I will go there and you two will 
 go with me. You will show me where he is.”

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:07.941
They came and the man was still alive.

00:06:08.606 --> 00:06:12.961
He was a little heavier, he had over 
 100 kilos. They put him on a stretcher

00:06:13.399 --> 00:06:15.340
and carried him. He said, 
 while they were carrying him,

00:06:15.340 --> 00:06:17.313
he remembered almost 
 every stone on the way

00:06:17.313 --> 00:06:19.557
because someone could shoot 
 them every second of this action,

00:06:19.557 --> 00:06:21.921
they did not know where their opponents were.

00:06:23.852 --> 00:06:26.407
And they brought him in and 
 the man survived, thank God.

00:06:27.685 --> 00:06:29.148
But why am I telling you this?

00:06:29.776 --> 00:06:33.014
As soon as the Operation Storm 
 was determined to start,

00:06:33.864 --> 00:06:37.650
the general of Operation did not know exactly

00:06:37.650 --> 00:06:39.715
where to go and how to go there.

00:06:39.715 --> 00:06:42.554
And because of this experience, 
 the officer from the earlier story

00:06:42.554 --> 00:06:44.447
decided to set out on his own.

00:06:44.447 --> 00:06:45.385
And he said,

00:06:45.385 --> 00:06:47.739
after about ten minutes of walking, 
 he suddenly turned behind

00:06:47.739 --> 00:06:49.495
and saw that everyone was following him.

00:06:50.131 --> 00:06:51.815
Even the general.

00:06:51.815 --> 00:06:55.759
They recognized from his attitude that 
 he is a man who knew where he was going.

00:06:55.759 --> 00:06:58.105
And in that difficult moment,

00:06:58.105 --> 00:07:01.218
when their lives where in danger, when 
 they didn't know whether they will survive

00:07:01.218 --> 00:07:04.411
or not, they went after the one 
 who knew where he was going.

00:07:04.943 --> 00:07:06.507
And he really brought them

00:07:06.507 --> 00:07:10.148
right to that school, he was 
 the first who went inside.

00:07:10.148 --> 00:07:15.046
He made sure it was safe and everyone 
 ran inside like they were little children,

00:07:15.046 --> 00:07:17.766
fell on the floor after a whole day of walking

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:23.582
and fell asleep. He didn't even have a 
 place to sleep. He slept outside.

00:07:24.773 --> 00:07:26.269
But he told me,

00:07:26.269 --> 00:07:29.593
these are the people and that means to be 
 a leader. The leader knows where he is going

00:07:29.593 --> 00:07:32.952
and the others follow him without him saying 
 anything.They did not follow the general

00:07:32.952 --> 00:07:36.285
who was ranked higher than the one 
 who knew where he was going.

00:07:37.404 --> 00:07:40.919
How will God reveal the vision for us to us?

00:07:42.911 --> 00:07:44.349
There are two ways.

00:07:44.792 --> 00:07:46.286
The first way is

00:07:46.286 --> 00:07:48.623
to enter a prayer and

00:07:48.623 --> 00:07:52.808
ask God to reveal it to us. And it’s good 
 to prepare for that kind of prayer.

00:07:55.698 --> 00:08:01.324
„God, what do You want for me from this 
 position right here? What more can I do?“

00:08:04.735 --> 00:08:07.632
And God will speak, maybe 
 on supernatural way

00:08:07.632 --> 00:08:10.887
like he spoke to Saint Francis: 
 “Francis, go fix my Church!”

00:08:10.887 --> 00:08:13.529
and to Saint Josemaría Escrivá:

00:08:13.529 --> 00:08:15.746
“Establish a congregation!”

00:08:16.717 --> 00:08:19.529
But, there is the second way 
 which is more common.

00:08:20.030 --> 00:08:22.400
If we become a man of prayer,

00:08:22.870 --> 00:08:24.870
 if we discover God’s heart,

00:08:26.873 --> 00:08:28.528
God may

00:08:28.528 --> 00:08:31.714
simply allow us to recognize 
 some need in our hearts.

00:08:31.714 --> 00:08:35.294
There is the calling of sister Elvira 
 who established Community of Cenacolo.

00:08:36.511 --> 00:08:38.319
She rode a tram

00:08:39.097 --> 00:08:42.170
from the monastery to the school where she worked

00:08:42.170 --> 00:08:46.051
and she saw numerous drug addicts everyday

00:08:46.051 --> 00:08:48.346
and that no one is taking care of them.

00:08:48.346 --> 00:08:51.133
An angel from heaven didn’t come down to 
 Earth to tell her to establish the community.

00:08:51.133 --> 00:08:52.482
She saw people in need.

00:08:53.828 --> 00:08:55.883
Jesus is in these people.

00:08:55.883 --> 00:09:00.678
Jesus said: “Truly, I say to you, as you did it to 
 one of the least of these my brothers, you did it to me”.

00:09:00.678 --> 00:09:05.458
Blessed Mother Theresa went to meet 
 up with Pope John Paul II on one occasion.

00:09:06.156 --> 00:09:07.338
On her way here,

00:09:07.338 --> 00:09:10.749
she saw a leper dying on 
 the road, stopped the car

00:09:10.749 --> 00:09:13.331
and took care of him. When she got 
 there, the pope was already gone.

00:09:13.331 --> 00:09:14.679
And they told her:

00:09:14.679 --> 00:09:18.385
“The pope was waiting for you.“ and she said: 
 „I know the pope was waiting, but I met Jesus on

00:09:18.385 --> 00:09:19.720
the way.“

00:09:22.313 --> 00:09:24.000
Sister Elvira recognized

00:09:24.923 --> 00:09:27.048
the need

00:09:27.455 --> 00:09:32.415
and established the community which 
 saved so many people from drug addiction.

00:09:33.223 --> 00:09:36.516
Jesus says: “They have eyes, but do not see”.

00:09:38.397 --> 00:09:41.345
The devil has poisoned us so 
 much through the media

00:09:41.345 --> 00:09:44.898
and through his lies and bad news 
 - that it is impossible to succeed,

00:09:44.898 --> 00:09:48.966
that so many things are impossible 
 - that we really believed in it.

00:09:49.716 --> 00:09:51.575
We have to open our eyes

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:53.834
and start watching.

00:09:54.746 --> 00:09:56.508
Opportunities are all around us.

00:10:01.603 --> 00:10:05.321
When my cousins came to Australia, 
 banished by the Communists,

00:10:05.321 --> 00:10:06.720
they were at rock bottom, really poor.

00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:09.541
They were walking in the desert, lived off welfare.

00:10:09.541 --> 00:10:13.278
God gave them healthy eyes to see 
 squids swimming in nearby waters.

00:10:13.278 --> 00:10:17.022
They noticed that Australians don’t hunt squid. 
 Australians weren’t used to eating squid.

00:10:17.022 --> 00:10:20.334
They started to hunt squid 
 and cook squid specialties.

00:10:20.334 --> 00:10:24.838
Today they have a fishing fleet of five vessels. 
 National Geographic filmed article about them.

00:10:25.669 --> 00:10:28.813
To open our eyes. To see. 
 We need to become visionaries.

00:10:29.697 --> 00:10:31.985
It is the father who must, in his children,

00:10:33.464 --> 00:10:37.117
and later in the space that God opens,

00:10:37.117 --> 00:10:39.819
be the one who gives life, who spreads the vision.

00:10:41.030 --> 00:10:45.337
God said in Jeremiah: 
 “For I know the plans I have for you,

00:10:45.337 --> 00:10:47.490
plans to prosper you and not to harm you,

00:10:47.490 --> 00:10:50.000
plans to give you hope and a future”.

00:10:51.680 --> 00:10:55.664
The real leader is the one who gives 
 hope and a future. He receives

00:10:55.664 --> 00:10:58.606
that future and sees it in prayer.

00:10:58.606 --> 00:11:03.450
Jesus said that the Holy Spirit, when He comes, 
 will lead us into truth and announce our future to us.

00:11:04.352 --> 00:11:06.098
He sees it in prayer

00:11:06.255 --> 00:11:10.949
and since he sees something he does not 
 have yet, he raises hope in those he leads

00:11:11.262 --> 00:11:12.701
that it is possible.

00:11:13.789 --> 00:11:18.055
This means to be a leader and every man 
 is called to be a leader, first in his family.

00:11:18.055 --> 00:11:22.004
And trust me, if you do it right, you will not stay 
 only the leader of your own family for long

00:11:22.004 --> 00:11:25.583
because God says: „He who is faithful in 
 the small will be trusted in the great.“

00:11:27.998 --> 00:11:31.760
Seeing something that is not there yet 
 and firmly believing that God can

00:11:31.760 --> 00:11:32.903
accomplish it.

00:11:32.903 --> 00:11:37.501
An example that shocked me, when I 
 mentioned Escriva, was how his co-worker

00:11:38.064 --> 00:11:40.665
described what it was like

00:11:40.665 --> 00:11:42.240
to live in Madrid

00:11:42.240 --> 00:11:44.539
without having bread for the next day,

00:11:45.009 --> 00:11:48.264
in an apartment with bomb-blasted glass windows.

00:11:49.529 --> 00:11:52.379
She woke up one morning and saw Escriva

00:11:52.880 --> 00:11:55.307
leaning over the paper and drawing something.

00:11:55.307 --> 00:11:58.256
And listen to the testimony of

00:11:59.364 --> 00:12:03.877
Encarnita Ortega, one of his closest associates:

00:12:03.877 --> 00:12:09.000
“Father Josemaria Escriva laid out a 
 map on the table, outlining the various

00:12:09.000 --> 00:12:14.776
projects that the female part of Opus Dei 
 had to bring to life in various parts of the world.

00:12:15.455 --> 00:12:21.454
At the very attempt to follow Father 
 Josemarie's presentation I felt dizzy

00:12:21.454 --> 00:12:25.716
as he explained all these projects to 
 us in an unusual and colorful way.”

00:12:25.716 --> 00:12:26.964
Imagine that,

00:12:26.964 --> 00:12:30.000
he had no dime, no bread, no rakia

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:33.626
and he said: “Construction of 
 agricultural schools for peasants,

00:12:33.626 --> 00:12:37.467
schools for various types of 
 vocational training, student

00:12:37.467 --> 00:12:41.775
dormitories, maternity wards in cities 
 around the world, the introduction of

00:12:41.775 --> 00:12:44.780
mobile libraries that will bring valuable and

00:12:44.780 --> 00:12:49.809
educational meaning useful reading in the 
 outermost villages, opening bookstores.”

00:12:50.309 --> 00:12:52.878
Folding the map slowly, he said,

00:12:53.506 --> 00:12:56.134
“There are two ways to react to anything.

00:12:56.134 --> 00:13:01.052
One is to think that all this is a 
 wonderful but impossible dream.

00:13:01.052 --> 00:13:02.211
The second is

00:13:02.211 --> 00:13:04.166
to trust the Lord

00:13:04.510 --> 00:13:06.710
and believe that,

00:13:07.273 --> 00:13:09.077
when He already asks us to do so,

00:13:09.077 --> 00:13:12.076
He will help us in trying to 
 make this dream come true.

00:13:12.076 --> 00:13:15.445
I hope you will react the second way.“

00:13:15.445 --> 00:13:22.632
“However, the reality at the time was 
 hunger, fatigue, weakness and poverty.

00:13:22.632 --> 00:13:27.033
We lived in Madrid overwhelmed by 
 the aftermath of the Spanish Civil War.

00:13:27.033 --> 00:13:31.828
The conditions of life in Spain in 1942 were 
 by no means conducive to the realization

00:13:31.828 --> 00:13:33.392
of such ambitious dreams.

00:13:33.799 --> 00:13:37.007
Escriva, however, was filled 
 with supernatural hope

00:13:37.402 --> 00:13:39.843
that continually propelled him forward.”

00:13:39.843 --> 00:13:42.546
Listen to this: “In the years that followed,

00:13:42.546 --> 00:13:47.199
all the projects he envisioned 
 in 1942 were accomplished.”

00:13:48.144 --> 00:13:51.232
It is living a supernatural life in everyday life.

00:13:53.999 --> 00:13:57.800
To let God build us, let Him 
 give us that vision we need.

00:14:01.203 --> 00:14:03.236
Building our character

00:14:04.112 --> 00:14:05.704
and prayer life

00:14:05.923 --> 00:14:11.403
will lead us to become capable, just as 
 Abraham became capable, to carry out God’s

00:14:11.403 --> 00:14:16.691
plan that will become a blessing to 
 many - from our family onwards.

00:14:18.502 --> 00:14:23.102
The greatest evangelist in the history of 
 Christianity, a Baptist preacher Billy Graham,

00:14:23.102 --> 00:14:25.415
who died in February this year,

00:14:25.669 --> 00:14:28.079
began his ministry

00:14:28.079 --> 00:14:31.922
by meeting with four of his closest associates,

00:14:31.922 --> 00:14:34.983
and they decided to spend some time praying

00:14:34.983 --> 00:14:39.310
in one town in California and to observe 
 the lives of other evangelists

00:14:40.387 --> 00:14:44.604
They studied their mistakes so 
 they wouldn’t repeat them.

00:14:45.601 --> 00:14:49.079
And they came up with four 
 vows they have made to God.

00:14:49.994 --> 00:14:53.827
The first vow was about finances. 
 Most mistakes were made with finances.

00:14:53.827 --> 00:14:55.347
They established

00:14:56.086 --> 00:14:58.300
a supervisory body,

00:14:58.300 --> 00:15:00.970
independent of them, to 
 manage their finances.

00:15:00.970 --> 00:15:05.142
When they tried to accuse 
 them of certain frauds, there

00:15:05.142 --> 00:15:08.361
was a report, a specific one, 
 with the entire flow of money.

00:15:09.137 --> 00:15:13.220
He died at the age of 100, without any 
 financial scandal. God rewarded their

00:15:13.220 --> 00:15:17.790
faithfulness and they became the most 
 financially successful church organization.

00:15:21.892 --> 00:15:22.784
Second,

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:29.135
they said they would guard their marriages 
 by never meeting one on one with woman

00:15:29.135 --> 00:15:30.544
who they provide spiritual guidance,

00:15:30.544 --> 00:15:33.519
because even David, the man 
 of God, had failed that test

00:15:34.708 --> 00:15:37.393
And there were always two of them or, 
 if their wives were traveling with them,

00:15:37.393 --> 00:15:39.178
then they assisted in prayer so they could

00:15:39.178 --> 00:15:41.178
make sure not to repeat the mistakes 
 of some of their predecessors.

00:15:42.189 --> 00:15:43.476
And God rewarded him

00:15:44.133 --> 00:15:45.742
by giving him a wife

00:15:46.493 --> 00:15:50.000
who is an example of a woman standing 
 by her husband and five children who

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:54.393
are in the ministry today and 
are disciples of Christ, and

00:15:54.393 --> 00:15:55.793
so are his grandchildren.

00:15:58.429 --> 00:16:01.545
The third thing was that 
 they would never gossip

00:16:03.120 --> 00:16:08.814
and criticize other people doing the same 
 work as them, evangelizing, but in a different way.

00:16:12.529 --> 00:16:16.911
And fourth, they promised that they would 
 never speak of success, how many people

00:16:16.911 --> 00:16:20.952
they had, how much healing happened, but 
 that as soon as the service finishes, they

00:16:20.952 --> 00:16:24.614
would obey Jesus' counsel, kneel down and 
 say: „We are worthless servants“ and commit

00:16:24.614 --> 00:16:28.705
to the next project. And they let foreign 
 media and others publish what happened

00:16:28.705 --> 00:16:30.000
and how it happened.

00:16:31.294 --> 00:16:33.148
God gave him

00:16:33.148 --> 00:16:37.006
to bring 218 million people to Jesus Christ.

00:16:38.057 --> 00:16:43.556
He had a crusade at the Seoul airport for 
 1,300,000 people who gave their lives to Christ.

00:16:43.556 --> 00:16:46.996
Today, Korea is one of the fastest 
 growing Christian countries.

00:16:48.260 --> 00:16:52.713
This was a man who had a clear vision. 
 He first let God build his character

00:16:53.557 --> 00:16:56.729
and that is why he conducted 
 such successful ministry

00:16:56.729 --> 00:17:00.000
and died at the age of 100 
 without a single scandal.

00:17:04.375 --> 00:17:07.764
And second, he didn’t impede God.

00:17:07.764 --> 00:17:11.118
He chose to believe in God to whom all 
 things were possible. The God who

00:17:11.118 --> 00:17:12.683
separated the Red Sea,

00:17:12.683 --> 00:17:14.154
who raised Jesus Christ,

00:17:14.154 --> 00:17:16.382
who healed eyes to the blind from birth.

00:17:16.912 --> 00:17:21.653
And what touched me the most, 
 some of you saw the video,

00:17:22.896 --> 00:17:24.832
in the time of the fiercest communism,

00:17:25.490 --> 00:17:27.023
in the 1950s,

00:17:27.993 --> 00:17:29.526
he came to Moscow

00:17:29.526 --> 00:17:31.142
when everyone fled from Moscow.

00:17:31.893 --> 00:17:33.333
And at the stadium,

00:17:33.814 --> 00:17:40.025
like Elijah in the moment he put his 
 head between his legs, in anguish,

00:17:41.724 --> 00:17:46.251
he began to pray for that region that has 
 been completely destroyed by communism.

00:17:46.251 --> 00:17:48.192
Before the crusade, he said that he

00:17:48.192 --> 00:17:51.553
had a vision and faith that he would come

00:17:51.991 --> 00:17:54.753
and preach about Jesus Christ 
 at that stadium in Moscow.

00:17:55.413 --> 00:17:57.597
And God rewarded his faith.

00:17:57.597 --> 00:18:02.505
What is incredible is that, in 1989, while 
 the Soviet Union was still in power,

00:18:02.505 --> 00:18:04.502
he had been doing a seminar

00:18:04.502 --> 00:18:09.846
there. US President gave him a permission 
 to go and he couldn’t believe what was going on.

00:18:09.846 --> 00:18:13.858
The Red Army Orchestra 
 played Glory Glory Hallelujah.

00:18:13.858 --> 00:18:18.269
I’ll show you in the video. Jakov will play the 
 video so you can see what was it like.

00:18:18.269 --> 00:18:20.554
He first appears in the video as a young

00:18:20.554 --> 00:18:24.960
man in his 50s. How did God reward his faith?

00:21:19.371 --> 00:21:20.630
…In His word.

00:21:20.630 --> 00:21:24.919
That is why we are often unhappy as 
 the two disciples who came from Emmaus.

00:21:24.919 --> 00:21:27.399
Jesus met them after his death

00:21:27.399 --> 00:21:30.764
and they sadly recounted to 
 him what had happened.

00:21:30.764 --> 00:21:33.047
And he quoted the Word of God to them.

00:21:33.047 --> 00:21:36.013
He told them where it had been written 
 that it must have happened

00:21:37.600 --> 00:21:42.344
and that gave them hope. They said: 
 “Did not our hearts burn within us while he talked?”

00:21:44.040 --> 00:21:47.415
We are often sad, unhappy, unpromising

00:21:47.415 --> 00:21:51.547
because we believe in our version of Jesus. 
 When we established the community,

00:21:51.547 --> 00:21:54.909
thank God for that, there 
 were only a few of us.

00:21:54.909 --> 00:21:56.777
We held our meetings in the 
 little house next to the church.

00:21:56.777 --> 00:22:01.214
Damir Zukan, a man with a distinct prophetic 
 gift, came to our meeting and prayed for us

00:22:02.438 --> 00:22:07.763
and he said: “I had a vision, God showed me 
 a picture – each of you came to your own Jesus

00:22:08.613 --> 00:22:10.022
and asked for something."

00:22:12.162 --> 00:22:15.041
That is Jesus from our 
 projection, who we made up

00:22:15.671 --> 00:22:17.339
according to our requests,

00:22:19.001 --> 00:22:23.365
according to the wrong pictures given to us 
 by our parents, often also priests, unfortunately.

00:22:25.450 --> 00:22:27.055
But this is not the real Jesus.

00:22:27.055 --> 00:22:31.155
That Jesus doesn’t have the power to change. 
 The only mold in which we are allowed to seal God is

00:22:31.155 --> 00:22:32.527
this (the Bible).

00:22:34.129 --> 00:22:37.724
And this man, from the movie, 
 decided to believe in the real Jesus,

00:22:37.724 --> 00:22:40.307
not what politicians and media used to talk.

00:22:41.352 --> 00:22:45.643
When he first went to Hungary among the 
 Communists, Jimmy Carter, the president, told him:

00:22:45.643 --> 00:22:48.285
“They will use you for their propaganda.”

00:22:48.958 --> 00:22:53.376
He said: “I don’t care. I’ll use them to spread 
 the Gospel because because that’s my mission!”

00:22:54.537 --> 00:22:56.074
He won in the end

00:22:57.218 --> 00:22:59.114
because the Gospel always wins.

00:23:01.655 --> 00:23:05.176
If you want to be prophets, if you want the 
 guidance of God, know the word of God.

00:23:05.176 --> 00:23:07.802
Some say: “God didn’t tell me anything.”

00:23:08.488 --> 00:23:12.000
How did He not tell you?! He said everything 
 that is written in here (in the Bible).

00:23:12.911 --> 00:23:17.198
And we have to get to know what is written 
 in the Bible first. And then what happens?

00:23:17.198 --> 00:23:18.887
The Holy Spirit

00:23:18.887 --> 00:23:22.254
will remind us of exactly what we 
 need in certain situations.

00:23:23.465 --> 00:23:24.676
Jesus says: 

00:23:25.082 --> 00:23:26.558
“But the Helper,

00:23:28.686 --> 00:23:32.361
“But the Helper, the Holy Spirit, whom the 
 Father will send in my name, he will

00:23:32.361 --> 00:23:34.301
teach you all things and bring to your

00:23:34.301 --> 00:23:36.597
remembrance all that I 
 have said to you.” (John 14:26)

00:23:36.597 --> 00:23:41.938
He will remind us. You all know the story 
 I have already told you, from Belgrade,

00:23:41.938 --> 00:23:43.916
about that miraculous healing.

00:23:45.520 --> 00:23:51.077
The Lord showed a particular Bible text, 
 I was obedient and a miracle happened.

00:23:53.994 --> 00:23:56.544
This is why the Bible is full 
 of contradictory things.

00:23:56.544 --> 00:23:58.278
In one place it’s written:

00:24:00.827 --> 00:24:03.683
“For whoever is ashamed of me and of my words, 
 of him will the Son of Man be ashamed when

00:24:03.683 --> 00:24:05.938
he comes in his glory and the glory 
 of the Father and of the holy angels”,

00:24:05.938 --> 00:24:08.188
 and in another place: “Do not 
 throw your pearls before pigs”.

00:24:10.015 --> 00:24:15.153
I asked the Lord why did He say two contradictory 
 words? Here you have to say that you are a believer

00:24:15.153 --> 00:24:19.083
and in another place it says: “do not throw your 
 pearls before pigs” – better be silent because

00:24:19.083 --> 00:24:20.869
they will run over your pearls.

00:24:20.869 --> 00:24:23.585
And then the Lord revealed to me that

00:24:23.585 --> 00:24:26.067
this is the way to force me to have a 
 personal relationship with Him

00:24:26.067 --> 00:24:29.100
and for Him to show me what 
 part is for what situation.

00:24:29.970 --> 00:24:32.598
The 21st century Christian 
 must become a mystic.

00:24:33.383 --> 00:24:36.179
Failure to do so will have 
 tragic consequences.

00:24:36.179 --> 00:24:41.370
I was shocked by the documentary I watched 
 about the 9/11 attacks on New York.

00:24:42.610 --> 00:24:45.997
Husbands, wives, families of 
 the dead spoke about it

00:24:46.452 --> 00:24:49.843
and they said that the vast majority of them, 
 when they had woken up in the morning,

00:24:49.843 --> 00:24:52.508
either dreamed that they shouldn’t go work

00:24:52.508 --> 00:24:56.007
or they felt restless or that 
 they should just stay home.

00:24:56.799 --> 00:24:58.560
But of course,

00:24:58.560 --> 00:25:02.259
the reason had prevailed and 
 they went to work and died.

00:25:03.506 --> 00:25:06.526
We must take time to learn to listen to God.

00:25:06.858 --> 00:25:09.799
What if St. Joseph, when God said to him

00:25:09.799 --> 00:25:13.082
that his wife and son will die 
 and that he has to save them

00:25:13.082 --> 00:25:15.638
by going to Egypit, said: “It is only a dream”? 

00:25:19.657 --> 00:25:21.750
We need to become supernatural.

00:25:21.750 --> 00:25:23.676
It does not mean to become weird.

00:25:27.961 --> 00:25:29.732
We must become mystics

00:25:32.244 --> 00:25:35.134
and we must start from the 
 position we are in now.

00:25:41.669 --> 00:25:43.866
This is what Moses prayed for.

00:25:44.457 --> 00:25:48.932
If you were at a holy mass today, you heard 
 that he cried: “ah, if all the people were prophets.”

00:25:49.473 --> 00:25:53.117
You know what is really important to 
 understand? We now live in that times.

00:25:53.871 --> 00:25:59.169
What was impossible during the Old Testament 
 - that cry of Moses for all people to be prophets

00:25:59.612 --> 00:26:01.538
- is happening today.

00:26:01.538 --> 00:26:03.713
We are living in a time of the New Spirits,

00:26:03.713 --> 00:26:06.655
about which the prophet Joel said: 
 “And afterward, I will pour out

00:26:06.655 --> 00:26:08.396
My Spirit on all people.”

00:26:08.396 --> 00:26:10.137
I personally witnessed

00:26:10.580 --> 00:26:15.318
that everyone, who have opened their 
 hearts, but everyone, I am not exaggerating,

00:26:15.318 --> 00:26:18.385
have experienced a certaing supernatural,

00:26:18.385 --> 00:26:20.681
extraordinary touch of God.

00:26:20.681 --> 00:26:24.365
And they have experienced that God is alive 
 and real. He touched them in their hearts

00:26:24.365 --> 00:26:26.211
and He gave them a clear guidance.

00:26:26.211 --> 00:26:29.650
And then, depending on their cooperation with 
 the Grace, it has been opening and spreading much

00:26:29.650 --> 00:26:31.021
easier than before.

00:26:31.021 --> 00:26:34.784
Previously, this was reserved for 
 the mystics of the monasteries

00:26:34.784 --> 00:26:37.557
who fasted for years to reach it.

00:26:38.020 --> 00:26:41.427
We live in the times of Grace 
 when God really gives to all

00:26:43.523 --> 00:26:47.173
who open to Him and who dare to believe

00:26:47.173 --> 00:26:49.556
that He is omnipotent even today.

00:26:50.423 --> 00:26:51.998
And what you have, as a Grace,

00:26:52.589 --> 00:26:55.624
is the priest and the parish community 
 here that have recognized it.

00:26:55.624 --> 00:26:57.291
Believe me, I'm going around

00:26:57.291 --> 00:27:03.120
a lot now and around Croatia, and I'm 
 looking at that misery. Here used to be this misery.

00:27:03.120 --> 00:27:04.684
Loss of perspective.

00:27:04.684 --> 00:27:08.139
I have already mentioned to you, people 
 were focusing just on problems. 

00:27:10.000 --> 00:27:13.549
This is where God has 
 opened one space. What I

00:27:13.549 --> 00:27:17.791
would like, after this topic, and through 
 our continued work this year is that

00:27:17.791 --> 00:27:22.118
you become a part of it. Just like 
 leaders, right where you are.

00:27:25.134 --> 00:27:27.152
And God will continue to proclaim,

00:27:27.152 --> 00:27:28.840
more and more clearly, what He wants from us.

00:27:28.840 --> 00:27:33.631
He first told St. Francis: “Go fix my church! 
 Can't you see it’s collapsing?“

00:27:34.443 --> 00:27:38.531
And Francis did not understand, he began 
 to make the chapel of St. Damian.

00:27:38.531 --> 00:27:41.070
He collected the stones and 
 started to built there himself.

00:27:41.070 --> 00:27:43.790
Then God gave him an extension 
 because he was faithful

00:27:43.790 --> 00:27:47.086
and said: „No, what I meant was you have 
 to rebuild the whole Catholic Church!“

00:27:47.086 --> 00:27:49.807
And he went to pope who was profane.

00:27:49.807 --> 00:27:51.471
We often tend to say

00:27:51.721 --> 00:27:55.368
that our church leaders are 
 guilty of failing things.

00:27:56.000 --> 00:27:59.539
They are not. The key is in our devotion. 
 Pope Innocent III was one of the worlds

00:27:59.539 --> 00:28:02.543
most profane popes and when he saw Francis

00:28:02.543 --> 00:28:04.039
he said to him

00:28:04.383 --> 00:28:05.572
to go away.

00:28:05.572 --> 00:28:06.823
He immediately chased him away.

00:28:06.823 --> 00:28:09.355
But God gave him the dream

00:28:09.355 --> 00:28:10.711
in which the church collapses.

00:28:10.711 --> 00:28:13.530
In that dream, the church was standing on 
 a rock and collapsing, and this little man,

00:28:13.530 --> 00:28:16.722
who had came to him, was holding 
 this church so it wouldn’t fall.

00:28:16.722 --> 00:28:20.000
The next day, he called him and gave him 
 his blessing for the Franciscan Order.

00:28:20.314 --> 00:28:22.865
Don't think that the enemies are beyond you.

00:28:24.218 --> 00:28:25.221
They are in you.

00:28:26.573 --> 00:28:29.329
The first battlefield you need to win is your heart.

00:28:33.730 --> 00:28:37.540
A friend of mine comes from a village in 
 Banovina that was completely razed in the war.

00:28:37.872 --> 00:28:40.736
The tank crossed the church, across the altar.

00:28:41.142 --> 00:28:44.142
But what was particularly 
 intriguing to me, about this story,

00:28:47.319 --> 00:28:51.591
was that none of them, before that war, 
 obeyed God's law. Everyone built their

00:28:51.591 --> 00:28:54.000
houses on Sundays. Hard physical labor.

00:28:54.000 --> 00:28:57.336
God made the chaplain 
 in that parish a holy man.

00:28:57.732 --> 00:29:01.134
He shouted and shouted from the altar, 
 “Build houses on Sundays and

00:29:01.134 --> 00:29:03.017
you will not live in them!“

00:29:04.769 --> 00:29:06.000
You know what happened?

00:29:06.630 --> 00:29:10.326
When the Chetniks of Yugo-army came 
 and razed the village, two houses,

00:29:10.585 --> 00:29:14.637
completely at different parts, 
 remained completely intact.

00:29:15.280 --> 00:29:18.000
These are the two houses 
 that weren’t build on Sundays.

00:29:20.110 --> 00:29:22.596
We can talk about enemies from the outside.

00:29:23.986 --> 00:29:25.948
Vukovar was flattened.

00:29:25.948 --> 00:29:29.077
Vukovar was the city with the highest 
 number of abortions in Croatia.

00:29:29.077 --> 00:29:31.402
They opened themselves 
 to the spirit of death.

00:29:32.784 --> 00:29:37.737
The drainage of the Vukovar hospital, 
 where the tragedy took place afterwards,

00:29:38.238 --> 00:29:42.000
was clogged with fetuses.

00:29:49.247 --> 00:29:52.908
The struggle begins today, because it 
 always begins from today and from

00:29:52.908 --> 00:29:56.194
now on it happens in our hearts. 
 Yes, I want to be holy, I want to be better.

00:29:57.076 --> 00:29:59.633
How easy it is to shift responsibility to others?

00:29:59.633 --> 00:30:01.565
Do you think that this what happens

00:30:01.565 --> 00:30:04.626
with Muslims in European civilization is by chance?

00:30:04.626 --> 00:30:07.378
If you knew Bible well, you would 
 see that this is not the case.

00:30:07.378 --> 00:30:10.000
As soon as Israel fell from the law of God,

00:30:10.000 --> 00:30:12.381
God brought from somewhere afar

00:30:12.381 --> 00:30:17.689
some people more powerful and numerous 
 who would come and conquer and destroy it.

00:30:18.753 --> 00:30:21.191
We have renounced the family law

00:30:21.191 --> 00:30:23.213
and those who are still keeping it are coming.

00:30:26.264 --> 00:30:28.244
Renewal must start from us.

00:30:28.244 --> 00:30:32.563
First from our hearts, then from our families 
 and then God will open up something you

00:30:32.563 --> 00:30:35.263
never dreamed of. Believe me, 
 I'm saying this from experience,

00:30:35.263 --> 00:30:37.643
not from a story or religious 
 education I have heard before.

00:30:38.188 --> 00:30:42.241
I had never dreamt of the things that 
 have happened in the last year.

00:30:42.241 --> 00:30:44.372
And I do not know what is coming,

00:30:44.372 --> 00:30:46.401
but I trust Him who leads me.

00:30:50.143 --> 00:30:52.394
You too should become his disciples

00:30:53.852 --> 00:30:57.381
so He could make you leaders by His heart.

00:31:00.174 --> 00:31:01.440
Amen.

